---
import MobileFeatures from "./mobileFeatures.astro";
import MobileMockup from "./mobileMockup.astro";
---

<section id="mobile" class="relative py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

            <header class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6 text-center lg:text-left">
                <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-white">
                    <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                        Seguridad
                    </span>
                    en la palma de tu mano
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-white/70 font-medium text-pretty leading-relaxed">
                    Asistencia inmediata para tus decisiones digitales. No necesitás ser un experto; VERA analiza el riesgo y te guía en segundos.
                </p>
            </header>

            <div class="lg:col-span-4 flex justify-center order-last lg:order-0">
                <MobileMockup />
            </div>

            <div class="lg:col-span-4">
                <MobileFeatures />
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>